{"text_id":113963,"tokens":["The"," quest"," for"," accurate"," data"," collection"," is"," an"," integral"," part"," of"," any"," research"," study"," or"," policy"," development"," process","."," In"," this"," pursuit",","," seeking"," the"," opinions"," of"," multiple"," individuals"," is"," not"," just"," advantageous",","," but"," often"," necessary"," to"," ensure"," wide","-","ranging"," validity"," and"," reliability"," of"," findings","."," The"," importance"," of"," this"," practice"," is"," underscored"," by"," at"," least"," three"," central"," reasons","\u2014","enhancing"," diversity",","," improving"," sample"," represent","ativeness",","," and"," reducing"," biases",".","\n","Firstly",","," diversity"," in"," responses"," ensures"," a"," more"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," the"," data"," subject","."," Every"," individual"," brings"," a"," unique"," set"," of"," experiences",","," beliefs",","," and"," attitudes"," to"," the"," table","."," By"," canv","assing"," a"," multitude"," of"," opinions",","," one"," is"," more"," likely"," to"," encounter"," a"," spectrum"," of"," insights"," and"," viewpoints",","," rather"," than"," a"," monolithic"," narrative","."," Consider"," a"," company"," trying"," to"," assess"," employee"," satisfaction","."," If"," the"," survey"," only"," considers"," the"," views"," of"," senior"," staff",","," the"," results"," may"," skew"," towards"," a"," more"," positive"," assessment",","," potentially"," overlooking"," challenges"," faced"," by"," junior"," employees","."," A"," diverse"," set"," of"," opinions"," reveals"," a"," multifaceted"," image"," of"," the"," company","'","s"," work"," environment",","," enabling"," more"," effective"," and"," inclusive"," problem","-","solving"," strategies",".","\n","Secondly",","," represent","ativeness"," is"," crucial"," for"," the"," applicability"," of"," survey"," results","."," A"," survey"," that"," gathers"," data"," from"," a"," broad"," demographic"," sw